1. *Predmet* je bio starinski sat. (The object was an antique watch.)
2. Ona je ispitivala *predmet* o kome je govorila. (She was examining the matter she was speaking about.)
3. Učenici su ispitivani o *predmetu*. (The students were tested on the subject.)
4. Oni su istraživali *predmet*. (They were investigating the subject.)
5. Ona je čitala knjigu o *predmetu*. (She was reading a book about the topic.)